## High-Risk Boundary Areas

- Treasury/custody/fund movement.
- Governance proposal/vote/executor.
- Trading credentials/exchange execution.
- DEX swaps/routing/liquidity.
- Marketplace settlement/payment/minting.
- Mining provider execution/payouts.
- Lottery compliance/randomness/prize/payout.
- ACS provisioning/autonomy/memory access.
- Wallet signing/on-chain writes.
- Production credentials/databases/users.

## Approval Requirements Summary

| Approval Path | Required For |
|---|---|
| BUSINESS_REVIEW | Non-executive classification, readiness package, opportunity/catalog updates. |
| ARCHITECTURE_REVIEW | Cross-nucleus contracts, persistence/API/UI, provider selection, ownership transfers. |
| GOVERNANCE_REVIEW | DAO, proposals, voting, governance plugins, federation or constitutional scope. |
| TREASURY_REVIEW | Funds, custody, settlement, revenue, billing, debenture, payouts or treasury exposure. |
| EXECUTION_REVIEW | Wallet signing, on-chain writes, trading, DEX, settlement, payouts, ACS provisioning, production credentials. |
| PUBLICATION_AUTHORITY | Public documentation and release publication. |
| PRODUCTION_APPROVAL | Production service operation, users, credentials, databases or funds. |

## Recommended Resolution Sequence

1. CROSS-REQ-05 - Portfolio Integration Assessment & Promotion Board Refresh.
2. Root global docs versioning and publication ownership decision.
3. Treasury/Financial Core ownership and escalation decision.
4. Business-to-AxodusAPP read-only consumer contract.
5. Owner-specific execution boundary reviews for Marketplace, Academy, Mining, ACS, Trading, Defi, Lottery and Dex.

## Recommended Next Request

CROSS-REQ-05 - Portfolio Integration Assessment & Promotion Board Refresh

