No integrations, APIs, product functionality, MCP services, providers, governance execution, treasury execution, trading execution, DEX execution, marketplace settlement, mining payouts, lottery payouts, ACS provisioning, wallet signing, on-chain writes, blocker resolution or production readiness were introduced.

